OL,6,BAre those torrid tabloid tales genuine 
OL,7,Bor gobbledegook? Club sifts through the
OL,8,Bjuiciest and finds out...              
OL,10,ETABLOID RUMOUR:EJohnny VaughanBis to be
OL,11,Ba presenter on the Big Breakfast, in a 
OL,12,B#250,000 deal. He will joinEDeniseBVan 
OL,13,BOuten in SeptemberE(The Mirror).       
OL,15,ECLUB 140 TRUTH:B"It's true," confirms a
OL,16,BBig Brekkie spokesman, "although the   
OL,17,Bsalary has been plucked out of the air.
OL,18,BRichard Orford will be going back to   
OL,19,Boutside broadcasts," he adds.          
