OL,6,ETABLOID RUMOUR:BEastEnders starEPatsy  
OL,7,EPalmerBhas had a nervous breakdown     
OL,8,Bafter being dumped by her fiance for   
OL,9,Bone of her best friends. The star, who 
OL,10,BplaysEBianca,Bhas been confined to bed 
OL,11,E(Sunday Mirror).                       
OL,13,ECLUB 140 TRUTH:B"It was an amicable    
OL,14,Bbreak-up, he hasn't gone off with her  
OL,15,Bfriend," says Patsy's agent. "Patsy has
OL,16,Bflu-like symptoms but hasn't had a     
OL,17,Bbreakdown. The heavy work schedule has 
OL,18,Bleft her feeling tired but she was     
OL,19,Bgoing to take this week off anyway."   
