OL,6,BAre the tabloids full of news or       
OL,7,Bnonsense? Club investigates...         
OL,9,ETABLOID RUMOUR:EAlex JamesBfromEBlur   
OL,10,Bhas co-written and co-produced a single
OL,11,Bfor sixties legend Marianne Faithful.  
OL,12,BIt'll be out on August 4thE(Daily Star)
OL,14,ECLUB 140 TRUTH:B"Yes, it's true, but   
OL,15,Bthe release date is the 11th," says a  
OL,16,Bspokeswoman for Marianne. "They met up 
OL,17,Bin London and came up with the idea of 
OL,18,Bdoing a track together."               
