OL,6,BTrifling or true? Club finds out.      
OL,8,ETABLOID RUMOUR:EDavid BowieBis to team 
OL,9,Bup withEPet Shop BoysBto write some    
OL,10,Bsizzling new dance tracksE(Daily Star).
OL,12,ECLUB 140 TRUTH:BBowie's spokeswoman    
OL,13,Btold Club: "It's a load of rubbish.    
OL,14,BThe only time Bowie has worked with the
OL,15,BPet Shop Boys was on the Hello Spaceboy
OL,16,Bsingle. They have no plans to work     
OL,17,Btogether. I've got no idea where the   
OL,18,BStar got their story, suffice to say it
OL,19,Bis the Daily Star we're talking about."
