OL,6,BGenuine or guff? Club exposes the truth
OL,8,ETABLOID RUMOUR:ERobbie WilliamsBis so  
OL,9,Bkeen to maintain his healthy new       
OL,10,Blifestyle he's joining a celebrity     
OL,11,Bfootball team. He's set to kick off on 
OL,12,BAugust 10th with John Leslie and Eddie 
OL,13,BThe Eagle EdwardsE(The Sun).           
OL,15,ECLUB 140 TRUTH:B"It's true he's        
OL,16,Bexpressed an interest in joining the   
OL,17,Bteam," says the Robster's spokeswoman, 
OL,18,B"but he's too tied up with recording   
OL,19,Band tour commitments to do so yet."    
